Description:
...

Usage: selectRouteBlk [-help] <name>
                      [-box <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury>] [-layer <string>]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<name>                           # Specifies the name of the blockage.
                                 # (string, required)
-box <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury>     # Specify the bounding box. (box, optional)
-layer <string>                  # Specifies the layer(s) and/or via(s).
                                 # (string, optional)